==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Caret
<hw>Ca`ret"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F., a species of
tortoise.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>The hawkbill turtle. See
<er>Hawkbill</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

